Từ điển Anh - Việt
◘['pleismənt]
*danh từ
 ■sắp đặt, sắp xếp việc làm

Anh - Anh
placement
■ noun
1》 the action or fact of placing or being placed.
2》 Brit. the temporary posting of someone in a workplace, especially to gain work experience.

Từ điển Đồng nghĩa
placement
▸ noun
1the placement of the chairs: POSITIONING, placing, arrangement, position, deployment, location, disposition.
2teaching placements: JOB, post, assignment, posting, position, appointment, engagement.
